~ A Scope registration form for the function body Form 4
~ The scope is defined as a child scope of the Global scope
~ This scope is registered as to be executed only once, and can throw errors outside.
Form Title: Scope Registration Request
Scoping Authority: Global
Scope Author: yetnt
Execution: One Time
Safety: Unsafe

~ A Scope allocation request so the filing authority knows exactly how much is expected.
