Form Title: Scope Allocation Request
Scoping Authority: (Refer To Form 4)
Amount: 1

~ A function body definition form. Form 6
~ Defines the function body that the function will use
~ This simply retrieves the value the parameters would have in the scope.
Form Title: Function Body Definition
Form Body Return: (As Provided By Form 2) + (As Provided By Form 3)
